<br>
I think the min hit is off, Crayno.  I'd wager the min hit on crush is 245.<br>
<br>
Here's why:<br>
DB = (bash min hit) - 1 = 200<br>
DI = (max hit - DB) / 20 = 1100 - 200 / 20 = 45<br>
<br>
I get what I think is the correct min hit from:<br>
min hit = DB + DI = 245<br>
<br>
Folks that have parsed this fight please let us know if this is correct.<br>
<br>
Final stats, Statue of Rallos Zek:<br>
DB = 200<br>
DI = 45<br>
